Note on banner images:
  The image files referenced via the `image` field in motto.json (paths under
  /assets/built/motto/) are NOT included in this repository. They remain hosted
  on tplegacy.net and are subject to the True Parents Legacy archive's own
  terms. The image PATHS in the dataset are CC BY-SA 4.0 (as data), but the
  image content itself follows its original publisher's terms.

